---
title: Chicken Cordon Bleu with Herby Broccolini and Creamy Mash
description: Close your eyes and feel like you're in a restaurant! Cream cheese, cheddar and bacon make a luscious stuffing for golden, breaded chicken breast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-cordon-bleu-fb8f8fc3.jpg
